'''Olin/Lands''' was a business organized by [[Ferus Olin]] and [[Roan Lands]] in the few years prior to the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], with their offices on [[Bellassa/Legends|Bellassa]]. It was established to protect victims of corrupt businesses by aiding them in creating new identities and finding new homes. It was a thriving business until the end of the Clone Wars and the rise of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. The business was shut down when the Imperials announced the warrants for the arrests of the two entrepreneurs, since Olin was a former [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]].

The office of Olin/Lands was located on a quiet street in the [[Cloud Lake]] District in the city of [[Ussa]]. It was adjacent to [[Dorma's Cafe]] and across the street from [[Mariana's Exquisite Designs and Alterations]].

